27:11.240 --> 27:13.340
Pejabat tingkat rendah.

27:13.550 --> 27:13.960
Betul.

27:15.310 --> 27:16.070
Baik.

27:16.720 --> 27:18.450
Kalau begitu, biarkan dia tahu

27:18.750 --> 27:20.750
